name: Etica
description: Etica is a community driven blockchain started in april 2022 which aims to fund open source medical research without intellectual property. All research conducted through Etica is patent-free. Etica blockchain is governed by two crypto currencies. ETI is the currency of the Etica Protocol implemented as a smart contract. EGAZ secures the blockchain and is the 'Eth' Ethereum equivalent of the Etica network.
